{"tid":1380543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SOGO上鎖關門   飲品店員工：驚警察多過示威者","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:43:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":100,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0a64c817abc3ac19b5cd92b99977eba7f397bd91","tid":1380543,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190729/s00006/42eb41b5bd71f3d53e2712edb2c329f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190729%2Fs00006%2F42eb41b5bd71f3d53e2712edb2c329f3.jpg&h=a4865ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190729/s00001/1564339071207/sogo上鎖關門-飲品店員工-驚警察多過示威者\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F1564339071207%2Fsogo%E4%B8%8A%E9%8E%96%E9%97%9C%E9%96%80-%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5-%E9%A9%9A%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%9A%E9%81%8E%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67bQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=12de4297\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F1564339071207%2Fsogo%E4%B8%8A%E9%8E%96%E9%97%9C%E9%96%80-%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5-%E9%A9%9A%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%9A%E9%81%8E%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85&h=500a8ca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190729/s00001/1564339071207/sogo上鎖關門-飲品店員工-驚警察多過示威者</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】大批市民原定參加昨午在中環遮打花園舉行的集會，但不久後人潮由中環遊行至銅鑼灣，並自設防線佔據軒尼詩道。銅鑼灣崇光百貨（SOGO）下午5時多已關門及上鎖。有其他仍營業的店舖職員說，印象中過往遊行鮮見崇光關門，但稱不擔心自己安全。<br />\n<br />\n人潮湧銅鑼灣 佔據軒尼詩道<br />\n<br />\n一間售賣特色飲品的商舖，昨午一直營業，職員稱印象中，過往遊行鮮見崇光關門。她說，未有收到指示需關店，自己亦不擔心安全，相信是和平遊行，並支持示威者。<br />\n<br />\n另一繼續營業的甜品店，30歲的職員李先生說，除8號風球外，印象中未見過SOGO關門。對於店外馬路有大批示威者，他說不擔心安全，若下班後便坐地鐵回家。他又稱，平日在電話看得多，笑言自己「都想試試警方施放的催淚彈」。他說，昨日生意與平日差不多。另一飲品店約7時關門。店內兩名職員關店前表示，不擔心外面情况，女職員又指「驚警察多過他們（示威者）」。<br />\n<br />\n昨入夜後，軒尼詩道及怡和街一帶，大多商舖已關門，24小時惠康及7-11則繼續營業。"},{"pid":"c4491de571d253e05b38c4bcab924af4a4c718d8","tid":1380543,"uid":60145,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"正常人講既說話  唔駛吹奏"},{"pid":"37032d6a34630ebda498e27b77b961016f4964d8","tid":1380543,"uid":20473,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"沒有嘗試過的人生 我都想嘗試一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ffc879f61ec38d25d93e829da98ce5041c9f66","tid":1380543,"uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"c4491de571d253e05b38c4bcab924af4a4c718d8","tid":1380543,"uid":60145,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"正常人講既說話  唔駛吹奏"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"其實根本90%市民都認為示威者係正義之師, <br />\n所以大部份都認同行動<br />\n又所以, 好多人係唔反對武力再升級<br />\n同埋見到義士輸咗會覺得可惜<br />\n<br />\n個民意完全站係義士一方<br />\n所以不論如何勇武<br />\n遊行集會係越嚟越多人"},{"pid":"a632ffc384875c4668dfcce34a1bc0510abb9db7","tid":1380543,"uid":282477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f8b924fa809b832d294a503f898a7cb32a0103b7","tid":1380543,"uid":131326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"毅進警察 社會垃圾<br />\n畜蟲小隊 冚家富貴"},{"pid":"48e0acfcd1b38df28a9e6821d330663c28b0f60c","tid":1380543,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:04:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"76ae7d9771a5db4381f5095480ebadda1e3bea6a","tid":1380543,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"正常人都知<br />\n我個黑絲fd話示威者搞事<br />\n我問佢。722你有冇出街? 727你又有冇出街?"},{"pid":"ed96f046aa9b3e488b4d9edbf15490a6dc119793","tid":1380543,"uid":211958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09ffc879f61ec38d25d93e829da98ce5041c9f66","tid":1380543,"uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"